%% Balance Query Flow: Bank/User check balances
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant BridgeAPI as Bridge API
    participant DB as Database
    participant BankAPI as Banking API<br/>(Open Banking/PSD2)
    participant Bank as Bank System
    participant Ethereum as Ethereum Network

    User->>BridgeAPI: GET /api/v1/balance?user_id=...
    
    Note over BridgeAPI, Bank: 1. Fetch Fiat Balance
    BridgeAPI->>BankAPI: GET /api/v1/banking/balance {user_id}
    BankAPI->>Bank: Query account balance
    Bank-->>BankAPI: Fiat balance
    BankAPI-->>BridgeAPI: Fiat balance data

    Note over BridgeAPI, Ethereum: 2. Fetch Crypto Balance
    alt custodial account
        BridgeAPI->>DB: Query crypto balances from ledgers
        DB-->>BridgeAPI: aggregated crypto balance
    else non-custodial
        BridgeAPI->>Ethereum: eth_call(balanceOf)
        Ethereum-->>BridgeAPI: token balance
    end

    Note over BridgeAPI, User: 3. Aggregate & Return
    BridgeAPI->>BridgeAPI: Aggregate fiat + crypto balances
    BridgeAPI-->>User: {fiat_balance, crypto_balance, total_balance}
